{{Top|canon=Sigil of the New Republic}}
[[File:NR_Seal.svg|thumb|150px|Insignia of the New Republic]]

The seal adopted by the [[New Republic Provisional Council]] as the '''Insignia of the New Republic''' was based upon the [[Alliance Starbird|symbol]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] that preceded it, the blue crest of the Alliance<ref name="HTTE Sourcebook">''[[Heir to the Empire Sourcebook]]''</ref> -which was in fact often featured in red.<ref name="ANH">{{Film|IV}}</ref> It was set within a circle of stars that represented the galactic community. The circle is trimmed in gold, symbolizing the right of the people to govern themselves.<ref name="HTTE Sourcebook" />

==Behind the scenes==
''[[Heir to the Empire Sourcebook]]'' says that the Alliance Starbird was taken from "the seal of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]",<ref name="HTTE Sourcebook" /> but ''[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed]]'' revealed that the Alliance Starbird was the crest of the [[House of Marek]] before the Rebel Alliance adopted it as their insignia.<ref name="TFU">''[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed]]''</ref>

